00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Chapter 17D 
She Was Only Nine Years Old 

00:00:10.380 --> 00:00:13.680
To the ringing of the bells we announce the opening 

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:16.320
of the first Festival of San Pablo’s Parish. 

00:00:16.600 --> 00:00:18.820
Please welcome our judges:

00:00:18.820 --> 00:00:20.100
Sister Juana!... 

00:00:21.720 --> 00:00:23.320
Father Beto!... 

00:00:25.020 --> 00:00:26.940
and Marina!

00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:31.740
This song is called I will praise you 

00:00:31.740 --> 00:00:34.000
It is performed by the Jimenez sisters.

00:00:34.740 --> 00:00:38.500
I will praise you, I will praise you,

00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:43.200
— I will praise you, my Lord…
— I hear this every day at Mass.

00:00:44.320 --> 00:00:46.700
The title of the last song is 

00:00:46.900 --> 00:00:48.620
She was only nine years old. 

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:52.840
Written and performed by Lucio Cantoral.

00:00:53.140 --> 00:00:55.440
She was only nine years old, 

00:00:55.440 --> 00:00:59.960
she was so pure.

00:00:59.960 --> 00:01:02.000
She was raped by her father 

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:06.460
and became pregnant.

00:01:06.460 --> 00:01:13.220
Violence engendered in her unwilling belly.

00:01:13.220 --> 00:01:15.600
Two persons helped her, 

00:01:15.600 --> 00:01:20.060
her mother and a doctor.

00:01:20.060 --> 00:01:22.720
Her life was fading away, the pain was growing.

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:26.860
Tragedy was averted, 

00:01:26.860 --> 00:01:29.640
an abortion was performed.

00:01:30.560 --> 00:01:32.800
The bishop rejected her 

00:01:32.800 --> 00:01:37.200
and decreed excommunication.

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:39.320
The mother was expelled, 

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:44.040
the doctor was expelled.

00:01:44.040 --> 00:01:46.800
Nobody understands this Church that can only condemn.

00:01:46.800 --> 00:01:50.800
The poor innocent souls,

00:01:50.800 --> 00:01:52.220
 who only wish to help. 

00:01:52.220 --> 00:01:53.740
This is a disgrace!

00:01:53.740 --> 00:01:55.378
Bravoooo!

00:01:55.800 --> 00:01:57.120
But Father Beto…

00:01:57.120 --> 00:02:00.640
Under no circumstances can a song defending abortion win the contest. 

00:02:00.789 --> 00:02:02.789
I vote for the Jiménez sisters.

00:02:02.789 --> 00:02:04.980
But they sing dreadfully!

00:02:04.980 --> 00:02:05.780
Father Beto, 

00:02:05.940 --> 00:02:09.600
Lucio is singing about a real-life case that was presented at the UN.

00:02:09.604 --> 00:02:11.604
Then let him sing it at the UN. 

00:02:11.604 --> 00:02:14.300
I am sure that that pack of atheists will give him every prize they have. 

00:02:14.300 --> 00:02:16.075
But in this parish, never.

00:02:16.620 --> 00:02:19.140
The nine year-old girl lives in Brazil. 

00:02:19.260 --> 00:02:22.980
She was raped by her stepfather and became pregnant, which threatened her life. 

00:02:23.480 --> 00:02:23.993
What? 

00:02:24.320 --> 00:02:26.240
Look, here is the case. 

00:02:26.320 --> 00:02:30.540
The archbishop of Recife excommunicated the mother and the doctor who performed the abortion, 

00:02:30.540 --> 00:02:32.469
and the Vatican supported him.

00:02:32.660 --> 00:02:35.000
It is inconceivable that the Church of Jesus

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:38.640
does not protect girls and adolescents who have suffered rape,

00:02:38.640 --> 00:02:41.380
and on the contrary prefers for them to remain pregnant, 

00:02:41.380 --> 00:02:43.380
even if this threatens their lives.  

00:02:43.380 --> 00:02:46.880
It is even more appalling that the persons who have saved

00:02:46.880 --> 00:02:49.560
the lives of the abused minors should be expelled from the Church.

00:02:49.720 --> 00:02:56.140
The Vatican State is obliged to respect the Convention of the Rights of the Child, which it has signed.

00:02:56.360 --> 00:02:57.600
Have you made up your minds?

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:01.960
The Bible says that children have the right to be loved, 

00:03:01.960 --> 00:03:04.980
cared for and respected, above all other things. 

00:03:05.140 --> 00:03:07.360
I vote for "She was only nine years old."

00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:08.501
So do I. 

00:03:08.501 --> 00:03:11.840
I would also like to add that the Jiménez sisters    sing dreadfully.

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:13.414
What about you, Father Beto?

00:03:14.260 --> 00:03:17.380
And the Golden Halo goes to… 

00:03:17.420 --> 00:03:22.600
She was only nine years old, by Lucio Cantoral.

00:03:22.600 --> 00:03:23.818
Here you are, Lucio. 

00:03:24.980 --> 00:03:26.980
Next time try to choose a less controversial topic.

